---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 506
  - Title: Shekel Hakodesh
    Location: 134
Tags:
  - Life-Love=Faith=Belief in the Unseen
  - 847
---
Happy the man who divorceth his desire for the glory of that which
cometh not nor appeareth; for no man will regret having stifled, to
the glory of God, the desire that assailed him!
